{
  "chapter": 23,
  "chapter_summary": "黄鸡大师、啸云居士、王一抓等人误闯峨嵋禁地，遭峨嵋道人伏击。小鱼儿以毒蛇护身吓退道人，趁乱掷出药匣制造混乱。铁心兰趁黑暗救走小鱼儿，白衣少女荷露与圆脸少女使展移花接玉功法制服峨嵋弟子。花无缺现身化解纷争，劝退众人。小鱼儿与铁心兰躲藏时被小仙女与慕容九妹发现，小鱼儿装鬼吓退二人，趁乱跳崖假死以躲避花无缺追杀。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_ji_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鸡大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当真是这里，你我还是快快退出才是。",
      "tone": "皱眉",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yun_ju_shi",
      "speaker_name": "啸云居士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，误人别人禁地，便是犯了武林大忌。",
      "tone": "赞同",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_zhua",
      "speaker_name": "王一抓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，各位就请快快退出去吧！",
      "tone": "截口",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_tian_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冯天雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大师且慢，莫要中了别人之计。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_ji_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鸡大师",
      "listener": "char_feng_tian_yu",
      "text": "计？计从何来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_tian_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冯天雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上哪里还有比棺材更好的藏宝之地？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何方狂徒，竟敢擅闯本门圣地！",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "擅闯圣地，罪必当诛，还问他们的来历作甚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_ji_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鸡大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是神锡道长？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_ji_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鸡大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣地之中，不谈旧谊，咄！",
      "tone": "冷峻",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这娃儿鬼笑些什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只笑你们峨嵋派自命不凡，却不过只是些不分皂白的糊涂虫而已。",
      "tone": "嘲笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说啥子？",
      "tone": "喝道",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么傻子不傻子，你才是傻子。我且问你，就算是咱们擅闯了禁地，你们又怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "机智",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "峨嵋山岂是容人来去自如之地，有人闯入后山，本派焉有不知之理。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是咱们闯入后被你们发觉，那也算你们的本事，但你们却显然是早有防备在此，难道你们峨嵋弟子真有未卜先知的本事？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这不关你的事。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这自然关我的事，只因咱们未来之前，早已有人向你们告密，是么？……哼，这人又是怎会知道咱们要来的，你们难道想都不想么？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，这一切都是告密的那人做成的圈套，好叫你我互相火并……",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "啥子圈套？哪有啥子圈套？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们只要住手，我自会对你们揭穿这圈套。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要中了这小鬼的缓兵之计。",
      "tone": "喝道",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，擒住了他再问话也不迟。",
      "tone": "喝道",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要害人的时候，却莫忘了反而会害到自己……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "随我来。",
      "tone": "轻声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "是铁心兰么？",
      "tone": "低声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "低低",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "如今我才知道你暗器功夫实在比我强得多，那种在一瞬间便能打灭十几盏灯光的本事，我实在比不上。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "打灭灯火的不是我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不是你是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yun_ju_shi",
      "speaker_name": "啸云居士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "居然有女子闯入峨嵋禁地，峨嵋子弟居然还在眼睁睁的瞧着，这倒是江湖中前所未闻的奇事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_he_lu",
      "text": "荷露姐，你可听见了，这峨嵋后山，原来是咱们来不得的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lu",
      "speaker_name": "荷露",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下无论什么地方，咱们要来便来，要去便去。有谁能拦着咱们？有谁敢拦着咱们？",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是哪里来的小女子，好大的口气！",
      "tone": "厉叱",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这莫非是‘移花接玉’？",
      "tone": "变色",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lu",
      "speaker_name": "荷露",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亏你还有点眼力。",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "text": "现在你总知道咱们是哪里来的了，你还嫌咱们的口气太大么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "峨嵋派与移花宫素无瓜葛，两位姑娘此来，为的是什么？",
      "tone": "惨变",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "足下莫非亦是来自绣玉谷，移花宫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子花无缺，正是来自移花宫，本宫中人已有多年未在江湖走动，礼数多已生疏，若有失礼之处，还请各位包涵才是。",
      "tone": "谦恭",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lu",
      "speaker_name": "荷露",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我家公子来了，这棺材可以打开瞧瞧了么？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "藏宝之事必属子虚，在下只望各位莫要中了奸人的恶计，而从此化干戈为玉帛，今日之事，从此再也休要提起。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_ji_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鸡大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿弥陀佛，公子慈悲。",
      "tone": "合什",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_zhua",
      "speaker_name": "王一抓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁若还想争杀，却让别人暗中在一旁看笑话，那才是呆子。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xi_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神锡道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢公子。",
      "tone": "唏嘘",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你不怕冷，你有本事，我可受不了啦。",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "受不了也得受。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九姑娘，好姐姐，陪我去找些柴来生堆火好么？",
      "tone": "央求",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你听，那是什么在响？",
      "tone": "惊疑",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，不会有鬼的。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算没有鬼，钻条蛇出来，也够要命的了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "有我在这里，你什么都不必怕。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人装神弄鬼？",
      "tone": "冷叱",
      "chapter": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "慕容九妹……慕容九妹，你害我死得好苦，我做了淹死鬼，还要做烫死鬼……慕容九妹，慕容九妹，你还我命来。",
      "tone": "鬼叫",
      "chapter": 23
    }
  ],
